Figure 8 Cumulative survival of patients after MI. (a) Shows
survival of patients stratiﬁed according to 24-h SDNN values in three groups with cut-oﬀ points of 50 and 100 ms. (Reprinted with permission[16]. (b) Shows similar survival curves of patients stratiﬁed according to 24-h HRV triangular index values with cut-oﬀ points of 15 and 20 units, respectively. (Data of St. George’s
